<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Bang on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/bang/</link><description>Recent content in Bang on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/bang/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Swift Error — Force Unwrap Crash</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/force-unwrap/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/force-unwrap/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="force-unwrap--unexpectedly-found-nil"&gt;Force Unwrap — Unexpectedly Found Nil&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This fatal error occurs whenever the &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; (force unwrap) operator is applied to an optional that holds &lt;code&gt;nil&lt;/code&gt;. The runtime terminates the app immediately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; operator tells the compiler &amp;ldquo;I guarantee this value is not nil.&amp;rdquo; If that guarantee is wrong, Swift crashes with a fatal error. Force unwraps are convenient but dangerous, especially with data from external sources. Replacing all force unwraps with safe alternatives is a key Swift best practice.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Null check operator used on null value</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flutter/flutter-dart-null-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flutter/flutter-dart-null-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The &amp;ldquo;null check operator used on null value&amp;rdquo; error occurs in Dart when the &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; (bang) operator is applied to a nullable variable that holds &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt; at runtime. This is a common error in Flutter apps that have not fully adopted null safety or use &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; without null checks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; on a nullable variable without checking for null first&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Widget &lt;code&gt;context&lt;/code&gt; accessed after the widget is disposed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Route arguments accessed without null check&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;State variables not initialized before use&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Future results accessed with &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; without null check&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Replace &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; with null-safe alternatives:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Bad: null check operator
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;.name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Good: null check or default
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;.name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Guest&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use null checks before accessing:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (user &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;.name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use pattern matching (Dart 3+):&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (user) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; User() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; user.name,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; _ &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Guest&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Safely access widget context:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;override
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Widget build(BuildContext context) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; args &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; ModalRoute.of(context)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;.settings.arguments &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; Map&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; id &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; args&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;id&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; Text(id &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;No ID&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initialize state variables properly:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_MyWidgetState&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; State&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;MyWidget&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;default&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// initialized with default
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;override
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; initState() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;super&lt;/span&gt;.initState();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; widget.initialName &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;default&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Error: null check operator used on null value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ProfileScreen&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; StatelessWidget {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; userId;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ProfileScreen({&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.userId});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;override
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Widget build(BuildContext context) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; Text(userId&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;.length.toString()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// userId could be null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: handle null case
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ProfileScreen&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; StatelessWidget {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; userId;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ProfileScreen({&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.userId});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;override
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Widget build(BuildContext context) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; Text(userId&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;.length.toString() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Unknown&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flutter/flutter-dart-type-error/"&gt;Type error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flutter/flutter-state-error-v2/"&gt;State error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>